        "text_e4wikT": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In 20 seconds or less with a two-foot-at-once foot scan, Albert Pro captures unmatched data about a customer’s feet, including static pressure data and the option for dynamic pressure.<br/><br/><br/>Fully integrated with Aetrex Orthotic recommendations for customers, the Albert Pro creates a profit center for retailers. It’s the most advanced foot scanning system offered globally and facilitates a more personalized omnichannel relationship with customers.<br/><br/></p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
